3-Tier-Architecture Three-Tier Architecture on AWS 📌 Overview

<h1>This project demonstrates the deployment of a Three-Tier Architecture on AWS. The architecture separates the application into Presentation Layer, Application Layer, and Database Layer for scalability, security, and high availability.
🏗 Architecture Diagram
image\Screenshot (98).pngmla
1️⃣ Presentation Layer (Frontend)</h1>

Runs on Amazon EC2 / Elastic Load Balancer (ALB).

Hosts a web server (Apache/Nginx) serving HTML, CSS, JavaScript, or PHP.

Handles all incoming user requests.
![Frontend Layer](Screenshot105.png)

